summary: Any Doctor Who fans out there on my IZ page?
title: Any Doctor Who fans out there on my IZ page?
body:
I’m working on a project inspired by the Tenth Doctor and I wanted to add some little things as a nod towards his companions, like a rose for Rose.

But what are somethings that would work for Martha and Donna (and maybe Cpt. Jack)?

I’m already adding their names in Circular Gallifreyan but I think it needs a little something more.

Any suggestions would be a huge help.
